            "description": "=== HAPPY PATH FLOW ===\n\nUrutan untuk test lengkap:\n\n1. Auth > Register (buyer)\n2. Auth > Register (Seller)\n3. Auth > Login (Seller) → token seller tersimpan\n4. User > Get My Profile → userId seller tersimpan\n5. Wallet > Create Wallet\n6. Listing > Create Listing → listingId tersimpan\n7. Auth > Login (buyer) → token buyer tersimpan\n8. User > Get My Profile → userId buyer tersimpan\n9. Wallet > Create Wallet\n10. Wallet > Top Up (10jt)\n11. Bidding > Get Minimum Next Bid → cek minimum\n12. Bidding > Place Bid (amount > startingPrice)\n13. Notification > Get My Notifications → cek NEW_BID muncul\n14. Wallet > Get Balance → cek balanceLocked bertambah\n15. Tunggu auction expire ATAU ubah endTime ke masa lalu\n16. Order > Get My Orders → cek order terbuat otomatis\n17. Notification > Get My Notifications → cek AUCTION_WON muncul\n18. Wallet > Get Balance → cek balanceLocked berkurang (settled)\n\n=== ANTI-SNIPING TEST ===\n1. Login seller → buat listing endTime 1-2 menit dari sekarang\n2. Login buyer → bid sebelum waktu habis\n3. Get Listing By ID → cek endTime bertambah 2 menit & status EXTENDED\n\n=== OUTBID TEST ===\n1. Buyer A bid 5.5jt\n2. Login Buyer B → bid 6jt\n3. Get Notifications Buyer A → cek OUTBID muncul\n4. Get Balance Buyer A → cek hold di-release"
